# Disintegration of kernels in finite spaces

We can write `κ : Kernel S (T × U)` as a composition-product `(fst κ) ⊗ₖ (condKernel κ)` where
`fst κ : Kernel S T` and `condKernel : Kernel (S × T) U` is defined in this file.

-/

